<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbe5d754e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s7642"><num value="7642">§ 7642.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated such amount, not to exceed $30,000,000, as may be necessary for the purposes of this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbe5d754f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/act/1955-07-14/ch360">July 14, 1955, ch. 360</ref>, title IV, § 403, as added <ref href="/us/pl/91/604/s14">Pub. L. 91–604, § 14</ref>, <date date="1970-12-31">Dec. 31, 1970</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/84/1710">84 Stat. 1710</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbe5d7550-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idbe5d7551-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="idbe5d7552-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Another section 403 of act <date date="1955-07-14">July 14, 1955</date>, as added by <ref href="/us/pl/101/549/tIV/s401">Pub. L. 101–549, title IV, § 401</ref>, <date date="1990-11-15">Nov. 15, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/2589">104 Stat. 2589</ref>, is classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s7651b">section 7651b of this title</ref>.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was formerly classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s1858a">section 1858a of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
